<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Thahsa Belam No</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. &quot;Nang ka Lalpau leh ka Pathien deih uh,
 Lopina leh chawihatna leh thilhih theihnahaw chu
 Kitupna zieka mu ding mawng na hi,
 Nangin thil bangkim Na siema Na deih zieka um leh siem,
 Chu ahi chiet ngal un&quot;

[V2]
 &quot;Belam No a thahsapau khan,
 Van lalchutphaha chûn,
 Zie khawvel vai hi hawm ina,
 Angel vamten a tiu.

[V3]
 2. Lalchutphah a chu leh A thilsiem te'n,
 'Belam No kawma chun vangphat nate, chawihat nate;
 Lopinahaw leh vaihawmna haw chu
 Kum khawsawtin um zing ta hen, a tih u chu ka he a.
 Thilhing lite cheng chun.

[V4]
 3. &quot; Zie puonvam silhte hi kuote a him,
 Khawilama kipata hung ahiu em?&quot; ti'n ei na dawnga
 Kei chun a kawmah &quot;Na hei&quot; Ka na tii,
 Aman ka kawma &quot;Ziehaw hi hun haksa taka pawtte
 Kha a hiu hi&quot; A tii.</lyrics>
